These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, sudoku, gardening, traveling
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, cricket, surfing, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is cricket##2
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
3. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##8
4. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | traveling  | hiking | gardening | sudoku  |
| Sport   | water-polo | surfing   | basketball  | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, kiwi, garlic, onion
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, teacher, software-developer, police-officer
1. the police-officer is not to the left of the police-officer##8
2. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
3. the person eating orange is the teacher##1
4. the person eating onion is between the person eating orange and the person eating kiwi##2
5. the person eating kiwi is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the videographer##7
6. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
7. the videographer is not to the left of the videographer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | garlic | kiwi          | onion | orange     |
| Job    | software-developer      | police-officer | videographer | teacher |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, security-guard, software-developer, entrepreneur
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, fantasy, spy, musical
1. the person watching sports movies is not to the left of the software-developer##8
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the security-guard is in an even position##4
5. the entrepreneur is on the far left or far right##3
6. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
7. the entrepreneur is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | dressmaker | security-guard | software-developer     | entrepreneur |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | musical   | sports | spy    |

