.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, trance, indie, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, basketball, handball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the fan of trance##1
4. the fan of techno is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
5. the fan of punk is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the fan of indie is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | trance         | techno   | punk    |
| Sport         | basketball | tennis | handball | skateboarding |

