3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person watching documentary movies##7
4. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the person watching drama movies and the person who's sport is cricket##7
6. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person watching documentary movies##8
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | action | superhero | documentary    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | soccer   | water-polo   | cricket |

