.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, 7up, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, handball, golf, parkour
1. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
2. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person who's sport is golf##7
3. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
4. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
5. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
6. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
8. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | 7up | juice | coffee   |
| Sport      | ice-hockey | golf | parkour  | handball |

