.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, disco, ambient, salsa
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, bike, van
1. the fan of punk is between the fan of salsa and the person driving the motorbike##2
2. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
4. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
5. the person driving the quad-bike is the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the fan of ambient is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the fan of salsa is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
8. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | punk | ambient | disco |
| Transport     | van | quad-bike       | motorbike  | bike    |

