3. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person eating kiwi##5
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating cherry is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
6. the person eating nectarine is on the far left##1
7. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

