.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, frog, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, tram, scooter
1. the owner of the rat is not the person driving the tram##6
2. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
3. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the owner of the rat##7
4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
6. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
7. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | mouse  | rat | chinchilla  | frog  |
| Transport   | helicopter | roller   | scooter | tram |

