.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, mouse, horse, cat
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, ship, helicopter, tram
1. the person driving the ship is not the owner of the snake##6
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
4. the owner of the horse is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the owner of the cat is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person driving the skateboard##7
6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the tram and the owner of the horse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | mouse    | cat | snake | horse |
| Transport   | ship | tram      | helicopter     | skateboard     |

 